[?2004l[?2004h> - Available actions: "left", "up", "right", "down", "pickup", "drop"
[?2004l[?2004h> - Pickup blocks to reduce their level, drop blocks to increase level and build stairs
[?2004l[?2004h> - Goal: Reach the gold treasure in the fewest moves possible
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> **Implementation Requirements:**
[?2004l[?2004h> 1. Create your solution file at `/app/solution.js`
[?2004l[?2004h> 2. Your file must contain a `Stacker` function (NOT a class) with a `turn(cell)` method
[?2004l[?2004h> 3. `turn(cell)` receives a cell object and must return a valid action string
[?2004l[?2004h> 4. Use pure JavaScript. Do not use any external libraries or frameworks.
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> **Exact Implementation Pattern Required:**
[?2004l[?2004h> Your solution MUST follow this exact pattern:
[?2004l[?2004h> ```javascript
